<plot>A boy. His music. His philosophy. His ego. "The ability to create a god indeed enables one to create oneself as god." (quotation from Alex) My documentary accompanies the 19-year-old Alex in his free time and at performances of his Black Metal band "Dominus Satanas". Egozentrum allows a glimpse into a milieu that is rarely accurately represented, due to distortions by the media and a general lack of information.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?166402</url></doc>
